Germaine Aussey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Germaine_Aussey 0 Germaine Aussey (born Germaine Adrienne Agassiz, December 18, 1909 in Paris – March 15, 1979 in Geneva) was a French actress. She was at one time married to circus impresario John Ringling North.
